{"tid":406420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老的士佬新錶扮舊錶偽造運輸處表格亂厄錢","createTime":"2017-09-19T15:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T15:49:42.000Z","uid":75373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1614c86952efc8cadb002b60a3ff60012bab01b","tid":406420,"uid":75373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"事關我前幾日搭的士 <br />\n車程百幾蚊左右<br />\n落車俾錢個廢老的士司機 <br />\n佢拎左張好似運輸處張表出黎話按表格上價格收錢 <br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢老：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你後面冇貼塊表出黎wor <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：有時後面唔貼 <br />\n（我心諗 點可能）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁你俾我睇你張表 睇吓有冇運輸處個logo <br />\n佢緊係唔敢俾我睇 擺低左 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我呃你做咩姐（d死人廢老語氣）真係按表收費 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁你落多次個咪錶 如果個錶開始係22我就按表格俾錢 我都費事屈錯你 （因為如果個錶開始係24姐係代表佢係新錶 係度厄人）<br />\n然後佢開始餚底啦 話唔想條數亂乜乜77 <br />\n我心諗死廢老收皮啦屌你<br />\n之後佢死死氣收我咪錶價就算 <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母果十幾蚊都厄厄厄 <br />\n我記低左車牌號碼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSN7*4* 想知再講<br />\n<br />\nbtw注意錶係咪錶表係表格 我驚混淆大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢張假表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/233739_e1b450a737dc7e2c4f11de30996c1777.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F233739_e1b450a737dc7e2c4f11de30996c1777.jpg&h=2bd67ab1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a858d430941ff4aa4a5bab11afbc2ad0ff0bf3e7","tid":406420,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:41:55.000Z","msg":"而家慣左坐的士一定睇左起錶價先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff3011a8518cafa4be54c0f0fcf6a7cadfe00c0","tid":406420,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"打星托咩"},{"pid":"1153887d1d17683cf189bfea5d61b34bae91bde3","tid":406420,"uid":25319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打星托咩</blockquote><br />\n咪臭是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb755433f32847befd6c194192ed0368546ff576","tid":406420,"uid":75373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打星托咩</blockquote><br />\n你想知我會再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}